  "about_title": "About Actuators",
  "about_intro": "We are <strong class=\"text-secondary\">Actuators L.L.C.</strong>, a decentralized digital institution building lightweight economic operating systems to unify and steer fragmented entrepreneurship ecosystems.",
  "about_desc": "We take pride in our team of engineers and experts who combine deep practical experience with modern academic knowledge. We don't just provide machines; we provide integrated solutions that increase efficiency, reduce waste, and improve production quality. From initial design to operation and maintenance, we are with you every step of the way.",
  "vision_title": "Our Vision",
  "vision_desc": "To be the gold standard for industrial automation in the region, leading the transformation towards Industry 4.0 with smart and sustainable solutions.",
  "mission_title": "Our Mission",
  "mission_desc": "To provide innovative and reliable automation technologies that enhance productivity and support the growth of our partners, while adhering to the highest standards of quality and occupational safety.",
  "values_title": "Our Values",
