  "services_subtitle": "Comprehensive engineering and technical solutions to enhance your industrial facility's efficiency",
  "service_1_title": "Automation System Design",
  "service_1_desc": "We design and implement fully automated production lines, reducing human intervention and increasing accuracy and speed in industrial operations.",
  "service_2_title": "PLC & HMI Programming",
  "service_2_desc": "Advanced programming for Programmable Logic Controllers (PLC) and Human-Machine Interfaces (HMI) to ensure smooth control and precise monitoring of all machine parts.",
  "service_3_title": "SCADA Monitoring Systems",
  "service_3_desc": "We connect your entire factory to a centralized SCADA system for data collection and analysis, helping you make decisions based on real-time facts and figures.",
  "service_4_title": "Industrial Robotics",
  "service_4_desc": "Integration of robotic arms into production lines for welding, painting, packaging, and material handling tasks, enhancing safety and speed.",
  "service_5_title": "Maintenance & Service Contracts",
  "service_5_desc": "We provide preventive and corrective maintenance services to ensure your equipment operates at maximum efficiency, with necessary spare parts available.",
  "service_6_title": "Consulting & Training",
  "service_6_desc": "We offer technical consulting to develop your factory, and specialized training programs for your technical staff to enhance their ability to work with modern technology.",
